{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Troupechief Balteid |image = Troupechief Balteid.jpg |caption = Troupechief Balteid |category = Normal Minor Enemy |type = [[Igna]] |level = 98 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Demihuman Gutter]]) |spawntime = Spawned by [[King Krawkin]] |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |healing = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate-front = |guardrate-side = |guardrate-back = }} '''Troupechief Balteid''' is a Minor Enemy in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Igna]] family, and can be found at level 98 in the [[Demihuman Gutter]] of [[Erythia Sea]], and is summoned by [[King Krawkin]]'s Royal Orders art. When summoned, it will use an art on the party and then immediately disappear from the battle. {{clr}}
